"{\"uid\": \"wndu.com-2024-07-31-buchanan-community-rallies-around-hannah-roberts-olympic-watch-party\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"BUCHANAN, Mich. (WNDU) - The love for BMX great Hannah Roberts remains strong, even after a storybook ending no one was hoping for.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 41, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9983014188911107, \"rank\": 0.0009135410664515759, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_Roberts\", \"score\": 0.9999999280564705, \"rank\": 6.764821173405791e-08, \"text\": \"Hannah Roberts\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_Roberts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannah_Roberts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Buchanan native anddefending silver medalistfrom the Tokyo Olympic Games fell short of medaling in the BMX freestyle final at this year's Games in Paris,finishing in eighth place.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Buchanan\", \"score\": 0.905592701415412, \"rank\": 0.10423894937896812, \"text\": \"Buchanan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Buchanan\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999780314968, \"rank\": 2.1968497840448197e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds gathered early Wednesday morning at The Common in Buchanan to watch Roberts compete.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event was reminiscent of a large watch party held for her silver medal run at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each rider got two goes.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first round, she ended up taking a fall.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The second and final round ended as soon as it started.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, she slipped a pedal on the first one second round, and it is enough to knock her out,\\\" explained BMX expert Rich Hoppe.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9983014188911107, \"rank\": 0.0009135410664515759, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 763, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"score\": 0.9780045106036921, \"rank\": 0.0217490620992404, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, she knew it, so she stopped it.\\\"\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While this is a tough loss, Roberts has so much to be proud of.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is a five-time world champion, a two-time gold medal winner for the Pan American games, and won the first ever X Games women's BMX gold.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pan American games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9983014188911107, \"rank\": 0.0009135410664515759, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many are looking forward to seeing her in Los Angeles for the 2028 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999995905556872, \"rank\": 3.2547412372802867e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud of Hannah,\\\" said longtime friend Michael Ruelle.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Ruelle\", \"score\": 0.9999998694743312, \"rank\": 1.3052555914198528e-07, \"text\": \"Ruelle\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Ruelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Ruelle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has been working for this her whole entire life, and she never quits, and she never gives up.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And even when mistakes happen, because they always do, she is still a champion, and she is still a hell of an athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 WNDU.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": []}]}"